# Redhat / CentOS installtion in VM

## Download CentOs iso
```
https://www.centos.org/download/
```
then -> http://isoredirect.centos.org/centos/7/isos/x86_64/

then -> http://mirror.linux.duke.edu/pub/centos/7.8.2003/isos/x86_64/
click on as the pic:
http://mirror.linux.duke.edu/pub/centos/7.8.2003/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-2003.iso

